## Technical Notes for Vercel Deployment
> [!WARNING]
> The current **Local File Upload** (Phase 4) stores files in `public/uploads/library`. 
> Since Vercel has an ephemeral filesystem, these files will be erased whenever you redeploy.
> **Next Step**: I recommend integrating a cloud storage provider (like Cloudinary or AWS S3) for persistent file storage.

